snippet.title: juliaplaysgroove
snippet.description:
Hi, my name's Julia, I'm 21 years old self-taught bass player, currently studying at music academy.
Thanks for watching my channel!

My gear:
-Sterling by Music Man SUB Ray 4
-Sterling by Music Man Ray35
-Sterling by Music Man Short Scale Stingray
-Music Man Joe Dart Signature Bass
-Kala Flame Maple U-Bass
-DR Hi-Beams strings
-Zoom B3
-Focusrite Scarlett 2i2
-Audio-Technica ATH-M40x headphones
